{"tid":1849881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國總統特朗普認為巴勒斯坦應建國 以東耶路撒冷某個部分定都","createTime":"2020-01-29T09:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T09:38:46.000Z","uid":70063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b55f9e9d6794e898eb3e8710ffab3239950298db","tid":1849881,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普公布中東和平計劃，認為巴勒斯坦應該建國，可定都東耶路撒冷某個部分。<br />\n<br />\n美國官員透露，美國的和平計劃較巴勒斯坦現時控制地區的面積，以倍計擴大。美國同時承認以色列在西岸的主權。<br />\n<br />\n巴勒斯坦表明，拒絕美國提出的任何中東和平建議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505353-20200129.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505353-20200129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=d8931109\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505353-20200129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd5ccfd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505353-20200129.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5c1cc543c6e57f04e3b7bb57cac7822a10fa28d0","tid":1849881,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"唔好煩，直接用白磷彈處決哂d巴勒斯坦人"}]}